 634:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @brief    Power Monitoring functions
 635:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *
